# ==============================================================================
# RVBS, PGS, and ASD Phenotype Analyses
# ==============================================================================
# This script integrates three related analyses:
#   1. Correlation analyses between rare variant burden scores (RVBS) and PGSs
#      in probands and parents.
#   2. Multivariate linear models for continuous ASD-related phenotypes,
#      jointly including proband, paternal, maternal PGSs and RVBS covariates.
#   3. Multivariate logistic models for binary ASD-related phenotypes,
#      jointly including proband, paternal, maternal PGSs and RVBS covariates.
#
# Discovery and replication results are combined using fixed-effect meta-analysis.
# The script also provides plotting functions for correlation and forest plots.
#
# Required input files:
#   - phenotype_file: phenotype and RVBS count file
#   - discovery_file: discovery cohort sample-level information
#   - replication_file: replication cohort sample-level information
#
# Note:
#   Replace the example paths below with your own local or project paths.
# ==============================================================================


